# Limits the build context Docker uploads on `docker build`. Keep aggressive
# so build cache hits are predictable and `npm ci` controls the install.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/build
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local
**/data
**/*.db
**/*.db-*
**/coverage
**/.vscode
**/.idea
**/.git
**/*.log
**/.DS_Store
